{"tid":134303,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Facebook 出現技術故障，部分用戶被登出","createTime":"2017-02-25T11:16:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T13:04:43.000Z","uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a5f532aafe57d58520ba1055b927b4bc354e60f","tid":134303,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T11:16:05.000Z","msg":"今天打開 Facebook 時，有發現突然被登出嗎？放心，這不是有駭客搞鬼，而是他們遇上了技術故隌，導致部分用戶被登出。Facebook 指他們已經向受影響用戶發出電郵解釋事件，並進行維修工作。不過似乎不是所有的受影響用戶都收到電郵通知，所以不難想像已經有人在 Twitter 上投訴了吧。<br />\n<br />\n昨天 Google 才因為同類問題重設了 On Hub 用戶資料，使得用家要重新設定路由器設定。所以說，網絡世界真是脆弱無比啊...<br />\n<br />\n經由: Engadget<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinese.engadget.com/2017/02/25/facebook-claims-a-technical-error-automatically-logged-users-out/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2F2017%2F02%2F25%2Ffacebook-claims-a-technical-error-automatically-logged-users-out%2F&d=0ZQOgT4XWRiGBLzCIZSXcjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=9163ab80\" target=\"_blank\">http://chinese.engadget.com/2017/02/25/facebook-claims-a-technical-error-automatically-logged-users-out/</a>"},{"pid":"9aa64a3d2bfedf496db6fb9efdf51adc1d6b32d4","tid":134303,"uid":71502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T13:04:43.000Z","msg":"最近fb好慢"}]}